725560f-a.title: Queens: 65th Place - Maurice Avenue
725560f-a.text:
(1)
65th Place, east side, between Maurice Ave., (left) and 51st
Drive (right), showing a rear view of J.B. Hyatt house and out-
buildings.
September 1929.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, at an earlier date.
February 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)
The same, showing at the extreme right a part of P.S. No. 78
on 67th Street. Note that in the last two views,the streets were
hnot constructed as in View Wo. 1 (a later view).
May 1923.
Eugene L. Arwbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
